{"tid":1777754,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今隻愛回家又講政治 黃撚到呢","createTime":"2019-12-10T12:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T22:39:09.000Z","uid":1734,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"694f847231dd12a44c9f296b634f8dddd152dc24","tid":1777754,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1c7832b7f4c2d8ecc0452981e0aa385e27425e","tid":1777754,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=072a4cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"17c6441a1e61cdf0ec8b6861a1b4c344eb7f6fab","tid":1777754,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"）"},{"pid":"c865697634e7b43131e10afe6bd5145539ab5bab","tid":1777754,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit